title: Episode 139: Gang Time (Feat. Trouble & Eric Bellinger)
itunes:title: Episode 139: Gang Time (Feat. Trouble & Eric Bellinger)
description:
Hip Hop artist, Trouble and singer, Eric Bellinger join the ladies of Lip Service this week to show you the difference between a player and a married man. Trouble shares stories about his "snackaveli's" while Eric explains when he knew his wife, La'Myia Good, was the one for him. One of Trouble's snacks even calls in mid interview!
